	<h1 class="title">为什么银行对 Android 付钱这件事没什么兴趣？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113378/small/113378.jpg?1435590009" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">周韶宏 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-11 17:03:27 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23559/medium/23559.jpg?1457514846" alt="" />			
	</div>
